            <div class="rum-item">
                <h3>KATALU RUM</h3>
                <h4>Fresh Cane Juice-based Rum</h4>
                
                <div class="glass-circle"></div>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Nose:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Fresh, vibrant, and inviting with clean, grassy sweetness, light fruitiness, and an authentic cane-forward profile.</p>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Palate:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Creamy texture with subtle citrus hints and natural sweetness. Crisp, bright mid-palate with exceptional smoothness and an airy profile.</p>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Finish:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Clean and refreshing with lingering notes of powdered sugar, lemongrass, and a touch of bitter lemon peel for structure.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="rum-item">
                <h3>BARANA</h3>
                <h4>Molasses Based Fresh Rum</h4>
                
                <div class="glass-circle"></div>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Nose:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Deeper aroma with hints of molasses, tropical fruit, and subtle herbaceous notes balanced with a gentle spice backbone.</p>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Palate:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Silky texture with richer body and natural complexity. Notes of caramelized sugar, dried fruits, and a hint of vanilla create a rounded flavor experience.</p>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Finish:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Medium-length finish with pleasant warmth and lingering notes of brown sugar, tropical fruits, and subtle wild herbs.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="rum-item">
                <h3>BARANA DARK</h3>
                <h4>Our Special Dark Rum</h4>
                
                <div class="glass-circle"></div>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Nose:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Complex bouquet of dried fruits, subtle oak, vanilla, and a touch of baking spices, complemented by the natural cane character.</p>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Palate:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Rich, smooth entry with notes of caramel, chocolate, dried fruits, and gentle wood influence. Balanced sweetness with depth and character.</p>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Finish:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Long, warming finish with layers of flavor that evolve from sweet to subtly spiced, with lingering oak and a hint of tropical fruit.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="rum-item queens-share">
                <h3>QUEEN'S SHARE</h3>
                <h4>Serey Lanmè - Treasures of the Sea</h4>
                
                <div class="glass-circle"></div>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Nose:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Luxurious and complex with deep notes of honeyed fruit, toasted oak, and warm baking spices. Rich with subtle maritime influence and tropical florals.</p>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Palate:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Incredibly smooth and full-bodied with exceptional depth. Concentrated flavors of dried tropical fruit, toffee, vanilla bean, and subtle dark chocolate with delicate salinity.</p>
                
                <div class="note-heading">Finish:</div>
                <p class="note-text">Remarkably long and complex with evolving layers. Warm spice notes give way to lingering tropical fruit and a hint of sea-salt caramel that invites contemplation.</p>
            </div>
